# Split the data
library(caTools)
set.seed(2000)
split = sample.split(census$over50k, SplitRatio = 0.6)
train = subset(census, split==TRUE)
test = subset(census, split==FALSE)

logm1 <- glm(over50k ~ ., data = train, 
        family = "binomial")

    method="class", data = train,
